# DeepSense 6G Capstone Project

This repository contains my capstone project based on the DeepSense 6G dataset.  
The project focuses on beam prediction in 6G V2I networks using GPS, visual, LiDAR, and machine learning based approaches.

## Project Overview

The goal of this project is to improve beam prediction performance by using multimodal sensor data and learning-based models.

## Dataset

This project is based on the DeepSense 6G Scenario 8 dataset.

Due to dataset size and licensing restrictions, the dataset is not included in this repository.

